name: Technology
description: Technological products or services bought for your business

name: Patents & Trademarks
description: Registered patents and trademarks owned by the business

name: Installations
description: Purchases of fixtures, fittings and installations related to buildings, like solar panels or heater

name: Land
description: Purchases of lands without buildings

name: Buildings
description: Construction of buildings and costs associated to buildings

name: Vehicles
description: Purchase of a car, including second hand or after-lease contract

name: Furniture & material
description: Large expenses related to workplaces

name: Plant and machinery
description: Machinery and tools directly related to your business

name: Other property
description: Other type of property, like plants, machinery or various equipment

name: Vehicle accessories
description: All accessories purchases related to your professional vehicle

name: Advertising
description: Publicity fees for your activity, including promotional material, marketing and POS

name: Exhibitions and events
description: Costs for attending or hosting trade shows and events

name: PR
description: Expenses for public relations and media activities

name: Shipping
description: Costs of transporting goods to customers, including postage and courier services

name: Business gifts
description: Under 50£ Business gifts to clients

name: Membership fees
description: Subscriptions to clubs and associations related to your business

name: Raw materials
description: All goods purchased as raw materials used by your activity

name: Consumables
description: Consumables bought and used in the context of your activity

name: Studies & works
description: Compensation and fees paid to other parties

name: Goods for resale
description: Goods you buy to resale later, as part of your activity

name: Social Security
description: All fees related to pension plans and social security contributions

name: Property tax
description: Local taxes that have to paid due to the ownership of property

name: Import fees
description: Customs fees incurred while importing goods from outside of the European Union

name: Employees compensation
description: Compensation costs for employees and manual workers employed by the company

name: Employers NIC
description: Employer’s National Insurance contributions payable to HMRC as part of staff payroll costs

name: General subcontracting
description: Compensation and fees with other partners that act as subcontractors or consultants for your activity

name: Other personel costs
description: Company's personel costs excluding compensations, contributions and vouchers

name: Office Rent
description: Rental fees related to your workplace

name: Water, electricity, gas
description: Bills from your water and energy suppliers (light, heat and power)

name: Office Maintenance services
description: Services related to the maintenance of your worplace, like repair or cleaning fees

name: Public transportation
description: Travel expenses done using public transportation (metro, bus, tramways, ...)

name: Car rent
description: Rental of vehicle, including shared services, but excluding leasing

name: Fuel
description: All fuel expenses for a car

name: Car maintenance
description: Expenses made for the repair and maintenance of a vehicle

name: Flights
description: All expenses related to travel by plane

name: Telephone
description: Phone bills incurred

name: Internet
description: Internet or hosting bills incurred

name: Office supplies
description: Various supplies and consumables bought for your workplace or office, like pencils, paper etc

name: Office services
description: All expenses made for your office or workplace that are not material goods

name: Postage and Carriage
description: Costs of sending mail and small parcels

name: Books
description: Expenses for books, manuals, and reference materials

name: Software
description: Licenses or computer services (like repairs or upgrades)

name: Recruitment fees
description: Costs for hiring staff, including agency or advertising fees

name: Administration fees
description: Services incurred for the administration of your business (excluding supplies)

name: Accounting
description: Bills from your accountant or accounting firm

name: Auditing
description: Bills from your auditor or auditing firm

name: Consultancy
description: Bills from your consultant or consulting firm

name: Legal expenses
description: Bills from lawyers, fees paid to the justice system

name: Exchange gains/losses
description: Profits or losses from currency exchange fluctuations

name: Sundry expenses
description: Miscellaneous minor expenses

name: Bad debts
description: Unrecoverable amounts owed by customers

name: Interest paid
description: Costs of interest on loans and borrowings

name: Bank fees
description: Nasty bank, credit card and other financial charges

name: Intangible assets depreciation
description: Depreciation of non-physical assets like software or patents

name: Tangible assets depreciation
description: Depreciation of physical assets like equipment or vehicles

name: Training and documentation
description: Training fees not including food and drinks

name: Donations
description: Charitable contributions made by the business

name: Entertaining
description: Costs of meals or events for clients, suppliers, or staff

name: Insurance
description: Business-related insurance fees for property (fire insurance), legal costs, and third-party liability

name: Other travel costs
description: Expenses incurred during business trips (Excluding Flights, Hotels, Daily expenses, public transportation)

name: Hotels
description: Hotel or B&B bills incurred during business trips

name: Bar & Restaurant
description: Expenses incurred when eating or drinking at bars or restaurants

name: Food: Reception & delivery
description: Food or drinks incurred outside of bars or restaurants, like receptions, canteen and food delivery, etc

name: Corporation tax
description: Estimated tax due on company profits
